content:
Batch Assign Agents to Shifts

Save time and unlock agent capacity with batch assignment. Assign up to 200 shifts to agents who are the best match based on your scheduling rules and objectives.

Workforce Engagement is available in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.
Shift Scheduling is available in the Contact Center Stock Keeping Unit (SKU), Einstein 1 Service Edition, and Service Suites.

To batch assign agents to shifts:
Shift Scheduling
OR
Workforce Engagement Planner

Open Shifts in the App Launcher.
Select a listview from the listview dropdown, and select Table View.
Select up to three months of shifts to batch assign at one time.
Click Assign.
Click Assign Shifts.
title: Batch Assignment of Agents to Shifts in Service Cloud
